thread.title: Jennifer Bargardi
thread.title_full: Skipper (formerly Jetaport) reviewed by Jennifer Bargardi

author: Jennifer Bargardi
title: Jennifer Bargardi
text: Excellent customer service! Rob took all of the worries and calling out of booking a hotel block for our wedding. We got a great rate and awesome extras, and I did not have to google search or pick up the phone once. I had one question, and got an email response within hours. Thanks Skipper!
